INCLUDING THE ELIMINATION OF POSITIONS. THOSE ACTIONS WILL CONTINUE IN 2004.



CHANGES IN GOVERNMENT LAWS AND REGULATIONS AND THE ENFORCEMENT THEREOF AFFECTING THE COMPANYS BUSINESS.

