

SECTION 1350 CERTIFICATION OF CHIEF FINANCIAL OFFICER

NONE OF THE INSTRUMENTS DEFINING THE RIGHTS OF HOLDERS OF LONG-TERM DEBT

OF THE COMPANY AND ITS SUBSIDIARIES (EXHIBIT NUMBER 4) ARE BEING FILED SINCE

THE TOTAL AMOUNT OF SECURITIES AUTHORIZED UNDER ANY OF SUCH INSTRUMENTS TAKEN

INDIVIDUALLY DOES NOT EXCEED 10% OF THE TOTAL ASSETS OF THE COMPANY AND ITS

SUBSIDIARIES ON A CONSOLIDATED BASIS. THE COMPANY AGREES TO FURNISH A COPY OF

SUCH INSTRUMENTS TO THE COMMISSION UPON REQUEST.

